#doc (Page) "zkEVM Formal Verification Project" =>

Accelerating the application of formal verification methods to zkEVMs to ensure correctness and security.

The Ethereum Foundation is running this project to obtain the highest possible level of assurance for zkEVMs, the end goal being bug-free zkEVMs. This project will feature a combination of grants and bounties, with the project likely running until the end of 2026.

This first Verso rewrite keeps the current project content but reorganizes it so the site can grow into a fuller documentation portal rather than remaining a single long page.

